{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_08_01_short",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 粗茶ですが、どうぞ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜と遙子のユニットバトル終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After Rei and Haruko's unit battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "病院まで付き添ってもらってすみません\nくじいた足を一通り検査してもらいましたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for making you come all the way to the hospital with me.\nI had my sprained foot examined…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6333333731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "足は捻挫も骨折もしていませんでした\n特に異常はないそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It turned out to be neither a sprain nor a fracture.\nThey said there's nothing particularly wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9333336274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3204537074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。怜がステージで転倒した時は肝を冷やしたが\n何事もなくて安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I was really worried when you fell on stage‚ Rei‚\nbut I'm relieved that you're okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0666669607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、過労気味だから大事を取って\nしばらく安静にするように言われました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ they told me to rest for a while\njust in case.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3000014384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 32.6771213848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "過労か……。ユニットバトルに向けて\n毎日遅くまで居残り練習をしていたようだからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Overworked‚ huh…? You've been staying late every day\nto practice for the unit battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4000014384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "無理してまた倒れたりしたら大変だ。念のためしばらく\n休養して、その間のサニピの活動は四人に任せよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be bad if you overwork and collapse again. Just to be safe‚\nfully rest and leave Sunny Peace activities to the other four.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666681051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 47.9557604154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私だけ仕事をお休みするなんて\nみんなに申し訳ないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't just take a break from work\nwhile everyone else is working. I feel bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2666681051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんにはユニットバトルの時に\n散々迷惑を掛けたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I already caused so much trouble for Haruko-san…\nduring the unit battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4333347718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0773700397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで気に病まなくていいんじゃないか？\n遙子さんだって、こんなことで怒ったりしないさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to worry about it so much.\nHaruko-san wouldn't get angry over something like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0333347718,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}